N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 4101.27 - Passes

State Regulations

No track licensee shall issue any pass, card or badge
entitling any person to free admission to its such licensee's track except in
accordance with section 324 of the Racing, Pari-Mutuel Wagering and Breeding
